      "comment": "DURAN PANTERA (3) comes here off a dazzling win at Gawler in 30.40 over 531m. In winning form and can measure up again. WEBLEC POLLY (5) is struggling to break through but racing consistently, finishing in the minors four starts on end. Last time out flew the lids with a fast early sectional but gathered in and finished in the minors when second (29.68) at this track over 512m. Solid beginner who can clear the tricky draw. Leading player again. BIG BOY JETT (7) missed the frame but ran a decent fourth at this track over 512m in 29.97. Harder here but expected to measure up. TRUST DEED (1) has a solid strike rate from this box.",
